summary: There’s just over a month ‘til I see tumblr user @taylorswift sing in Indianapolis (FL E, Row 26, Seat 28) on her reputation...
body:
So since…

There’s just over a month ‘til I see tumblr user @taylorswift sing in Indianapolis (FL E, Row 26, Seat 28) on her reputation Stadium Tour, I thought I’d take a trip down memory lane of my life as a swiftie leading up to the day of the show!!

Throwback to March 15, 2015 for my 14th birthday when I got the 1989 album cover as my cake!! The baker didn’t rly understand that it was meant to be a polaroid but that’s alright bc look at the detail! In Botswana we didn’t really have access to fondant printing so she had her husband paint Taylor on!!!

summary: This is someone who I would fight for to see @taylorswift @taylornation . I would give up my spot for Laura without a moments...
body: This is someone who I would fight for to see @taylorswift @taylornation . I would give up my spot for Laura without a moments hesitation. THIS is what being a swiftie is all about. Not this bitchiness, this wanting to have the most followers, this clique who only talk to each other as if we are back in high school like WHAT EW. Not commenting on posts saying follow for follow or whatever. Follow someone cause you want to. Follow swifties back cause you want to. Be kind, caring, compassionate, generous, like @taylorswift is. God I can’t say it enough. How y’all are acting is the opposite of what Taylor wants to leave behind as her legacy. I came on here to make friends and i am glad I found some really good ones but far out, it’s a mess out there - here, Twitter, idk tumblr I can’t even see what goes on half the time but people arguing is going on everywhere. This is perspective. You have such a beautiful soul and outlook on life @lauraa.jamess, I wish I was half the person you were. Half has brave and courageous and beautiful. I will do everything in my power to help you meet Taylor and I know so many others will too. ❤️
